# Optimization #1: Pool Response structs

## Implementation
- Added sync.Pool for Response structs in meta/reader.go
- Added GetResponse() and PutResponse() functions
- Updated ReadResponse to use pooled responses
- Updated all client methods to return responses to pool after use
- Added defer meta.PutResponse(resp) in Get, Set, Add, Delete, Increment, healthCheck
- Required copying value data in Get since response is returned to pool

